---
import Base from "$layout/Base.astro";
---

<Base class="page-void" name="404" description="The page could not be found">
  <header>
    <h1 class="title">404</h1>
    <p>That means the page or resource can not be found here!</p>
  </header>
  <main>
    <details>
      <summary>I expected something here</summary>
      I probably messed up. Tell me about it.<br />
      I mean, really do tell me about it,
      preferably over on the
      <a href="https://github.com/thegatesdev/thegates.dev/issues"
        >GitHub issue tracker</a
      >.
    </details>
    <details>
      <summary>Pineapple goes on pizza</summary>
      Just don't be a picky eater.
    </details>
  </main>
</Base>

<style is:global>
  .page-void {
    max-width: 40rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1rem;

    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: var(--space-section-2);
  }
  .page-void header {
    margin-top: 40vh;
  }
</style>
